    <h1 class="m-0 mb-3 mx-auto max-w-[20ch] leading-[1.03] text-5xl sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl serif">Your car is an asset. Make it pay you back.</h1>
    <p class="m-0 mx-auto max-w-[52ch] leading-relaxed text-lg text-[color:var(--text-secondary)]">Become a Drivly host in under 10 minutes. We handle the insurance, payments, and roadside. You hand off keys.</p>
